article_title: Can homeless shelter survive without 'Street Ed'?
article_text:
Kankakee, IL (60901)

Today

Variable clouds with thunderstorms, especially in the morning. High 86F. Winds SSW at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening, then cloudy skies overnight. Low 66F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 40%.
